Hello,
I was expecting kbuild passes CONFIG_FOO from .config to CC
-DCONFIG_FOO, but it doesn't.  So I have to add
ifdef CONFIG_FOO
EXTRA_CFLAGS += -DCONFIG_FOO
endif
Is that the right way? thanks in advance.
